txt.en: The Fangorn Web-hunters are deep in the Silkenhold, lurking in wait to destroy their prey.
The Fangorn Web-hunters are deep in the Silkenhold, lurking in wait to destroy their prey.
Fangorn Web-hunters can be found in the furthest reaches of the Silkenhold.\n\nAfter defeating the spinners, the web-hunters ought to be your next prey.

You have defeated a great many spiders in the Silkenhold of Fangorn, helping to stop the spread of evil in this land. Your good deeds will have lasting effects upon the Ents and other creatures of the forest.
